frame Join a battle

actor Student
activate Student

Student->System: 1: requestBattlePage()
activate System
System-->Student: 2: show(battle-page)
deactivate System

Student->System: 3: joinBattle(battle)
activate System
alt signIn == false
System-->Student: 4: show(not-signed-in Message)
else alreadyJoined == true
System-->Student: 5: show(already-joined Message)
else
System->System: 6: createNewTeam(student)
Student<--System: 7: ack
end

deactivate System
deactivate Student

